_meta.llm_purpose: Recipe LLM for enchanting - creates enchantment/adornment recipes

values: Advanced durability enchantment using diamond. Nearly indestructible.
Advanced efficiency using storm essence. Tools blur with speed.
Advanced protection using golem essence. Stone-like resilience.
Basic durability enchantment. Items last longer before needing repair.
Basic sharpening enchantment using fire crystals. The edge never dulls.
Efficiency enchantment for tools. Gather resources faster.
Fire enchantment for weapons. Strikes leave burning wounds.
Fortune enchantment for tools. Better yields from resources.
Frost enchantment for weapons. Enemies slow and freeze.
Improved sharpening using lightning shards. The blade crackles with energy.
Knockback enchantment. Send enemies flying with each hit.
Lifesteal enchantment. Drain life from enemies with each strike.
Lightning enchantment for weapons. Chain attacks to nearby enemies.
Master fortune using chaos essence. Reality bends toward abundance.
Master protection with void essence. Damage dissipates into nothing.
Master sharpening using phoenix ash. The edge exists between states of matter.
Poison enchantment. Attacks inflict lingering toxins.
Regeneration enchantment. Slowly heal over time.
Self-repair enchantment. Items slowly fix themselves over time.
Silk touch enchantment. Harvest blocks exactly as they are.
Soul bound enchantment. Item returns to you upon death.
Speed enchantment. Move faster while wearing this armor.
Weightless enchantment. Items become lighter without losing strength.

metadata.narrative: Speed enchantment. Move faster while wearing this armor.
